| chinky    | Reddy    | Karimnagar | Karimnagar | Telangana | 505001 | 9849343893  | chinky123@gmail.com |
| Mansi     | Reddy    | Karimnagar | Karimnagar | Telangana | 505001 | 9999999992  | mansi123@gmail.com  |
