---------------------------------------------------------------UC-4------------------------------------------------------
Ability to edit existing contact person using their name
---------------------------------------------------------------UC-4------------------------------------------------------

mysql>  update addressbook set PhoneNumber = '9949717712' where FirstName = 'Pinky';
Query OK, 1 row affected (0.01 sec)
Rows matched: 1  Changed: 1  Warnings: 0

